  "description": "<p><strong>Outdoor Sales Executive</strong></p><ul><li>Mon to Fri 830am-530pm, Sat 830am - 1230pm (Alt Sat work)</li><li>Basic $2800 to $3200 + $1400 Transport Allowances + Commissions</li><li>Address:Joo Koon</li><li>Posses with valid class 3 license and own vehicle</li></ul><p><strong>Items selling - Fasteners and related Engineering Products to Civil and Structure / Construction / Oag Industry</strong><br /><strong> </strong><br /><strong>Job description:</strong></p><ul><li>Outdoor sales role in meeting clients or customers in promoting company's product.</li><li>Conduct calls and face-to-face meetings with customers daily.</li><li>Build and maintain relationships with new and repeat customers.</li><li>Maintain records of all sales leads and customer accounts.</li><li>Educate customers on how products or services can benefit them financially and professionally.</li></ul><p>Samuel Siaw</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd</p><p>EA No: 14C7279</p><p>Reg No: R2412474</p><p></p>",
